							       Instant Payment has been used on invoice no. {{ invoice_number }} sent by {{ company_name }}. <br/><br/> We have sent {{ factoring_amount }} kr. to your bank account ending with {{ account_number }} and prepared the book keeping for you, which you just have to approve in e-conomic. You can expect payment within 2 hours (weekdays, between 8am and 6pm).<br/><br/>Attached to this email is the receipt for the sale. 
            </mj-text>
     		</mj-column>
   	</mj-section>
 </mj-wrapper>
  
